data.description: Welcome to the beautifully maintained custom home. When you walk up you will notice the large front porch with a custom front door. As you walk in, you are greeted with the the living room with views to the backyard and covered deck for relaxing. The living room features a gas fireplace surrounded with plenty of shelving and cabinets with granite countertops. This opens up to the dining room and kitchen adorned with wood grained appearing tile. All upgraded lighting fixtures and custom blinds throughout. The kitchen features all granite countertops including the island which houses a copper sink. Upgraded appliances and faucets noted in the kitchen. Off of the kitchen is a separate laundry room with custom built pedestals for the washer and dryer. Split bedroom plan with the master bedroom located on the south side of the home. Vaulted ceilings with a dark accent wall to complement the space. Barn door entry to the master bathroom. In the bathroom you will notice 2 separate closets, dual sinks with upgraded faucets, separate soaker tub, and a full tile shower with two shower heads. On the other end of the home you have 2 bedrooms and a full bathroom with granite countertops. In the basement, you will noticed a freshly painted extra large family room complete with view out windows, a second gas fireplace, and a full wet bar with tile backsplash and custom shelving. Also in the basement is two additional bedrooms and a full bathroom. Out back, you have a covered deck with stairs down to a concrete patio. Very large backyard with a sprinkler system and irrigation well. Concrete pad already laid if you choose to place a storage shed. All exterior doors, include the door to the garage are equipped with upgraded storm doors. Come check out this beautiful home that is even better in person than the pictures!
